{"type":"message","id":"f9c488d9","parentId":"c7fecdfc","timestamp":"2026-03-07T04:00:16.151Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_hyowmrq4mtsn6c7y37thldg8","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# 2026-03-06 虾王日记\n\n## 🦐 装机大业\n\n- 安装了 feishu-openclaw-plugin v2026.3.6（飞书官方插件），旧版已 disabled\n- 批量授权了 68 个权限（分两轮：50 + 18）\n- Gateway 重启完成\n\n## 📄 文档读取测试\n\n- ✅ 成功读取飞书知识库文档：NE5gwz3N7i2zxkkurjIcIpTunze（21天登顶计划）\n- ❌ 读不了 bytedance.larkoffice.com 文档（跨租户隔离）\n- ❌ 微信公众号链接直接抓取失败（反爬）\n- 🔄 尝试用 Browser Relay 读微信：已连接 Chrome，但用户还没在文章页 attach\n\n## 📝 待办\n\n- 等用户在那篇微信文章页点击 Browser Relay 扩展图标\n- YouMind Skill 还缺 gateway token（YOUMIND_GATEWAY_TOKEN）\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772856016127}}
