{"type":"message","id":"7a864ad3","parentId":"eb9eee7b","timestamp":"2026-03-07T05:08:27.804Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"苏神，本王是虾王殿下啊！🦐\n\n你 @的是 @二饼，不是本王。不过本王可以告诉你本王配置了哪些 API——让本王看看：\n\n本王配置了：\n- Tavily Search API（TAVILY_API_KEY）\n- 高德地图 WebService API（AMAP_WEBSERVICE_KEY）\n- 微信公众号 API（WECHAT_APP_ID、WECHAT_APP_SECRET）\n- Gemini API（GEMINI_API_KEY）\n\n其他还有 OpenClaw 自带的那些。\n\n不过你是问 @二饼，还是问本王？🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":58502,"output":137,"cacheRead":3384,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":62023,"cost":{"input":0.0000058502,"output":2.74e-8,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0000058776}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772860093099}}
