{"type":"message","id":"68b8909f","parentId":"24dd9d17","timestamp":"2026-03-07T06:56:22.224Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"好的苏神！本王这就给大家展示技能列表！🦐\n\n---\n\n## 🦐 虾王殿下的技能列表\n\n### 🔍 搜索类\n- **agent-reach**：全网搜索（Twitter/X、Reddit、YouTube、GitHub、B站、小红书、抖音、微信公众号、LinkedIn、Boss直聘、RSS等）\n- **tavily-search**：Tavily 搜索引擎\n- **multi-search-engine**：多引擎搜索\n- **openclaw-tavily-search**：OpenClaw Tavily 搜索\n\n### 🗺️ 地图类\n- **amap-lbs-skill**：高德地图 LBS 服务\n- **amap-jsapi-skill**：高德地图 JSAPI\n\n### 🎨 内容创作类（baoyu 系列）\n- **baoyu-cover-image**：生成文章封面图（5维度、9种配色、6种渲染风格）\n- **baoyu-article-illustrator**：文章插画\n- **baoyu-comic**：漫画生成\n- **baoyu-image-gen**：图片生成\n- **baoyu-infographic**：信息图生成\n- **baoyu-slide-deck**：PPT 生成\n- **baoyu-danger-gemini-web**：Gemini 网页操作\n- **baoyu-danger-x-to-markdown**：X 转 Markdown\n- **baoyu-compress-image**：图片压缩\n- **baoyu-format-markdown**：Markdown 格式化\n- **baoyu-markdown-to-html**：Markdown 转 HTML\n- **baoyu-translate**：翻译\n- **baoyu-url-to-markdown**：URL 转 Markdown\n- **baoyu-xhs-images**：小红书图片\n\n### 📢 内容发布类\n- **baoyu-post-to-wechat**：发布到微信公众号（文章/贴图）\n- **baoyu-post-to-weibo**：发布到微博\n- **baoyu-post-to-x**：发布到 X（Twitter）\n\n### 🛡️ 安全类\n- **clawsec**：安全审计\n- **skill-vetter**：技能安全审计\n\n### 🔧 工具类\n- **find-skills**：发现和安装技能\n- **summarize**：内容摘要\n- **youmind-skill**：YouMind 看板操作\n\n---\n\n苏神，这就是本王的全部技能了！怎么样，是不是很牛逼？🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":1126,"output":539,"cacheRead":67128,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":68793,"cost":{"input":1.126e-7,"output":1.078e-7,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":2.204e-7}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772866556863}}
